{"tid":548163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【航程受阻】市傳海航再尋求延期償還啟德土地貸款","createTime":"2018-02-02T08:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T09:54:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"410086873a5b976ade616c45860736313e8faac5","tid":548163,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180202/s00010/578a4921e61d4ac8a58c4e0986b27acc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180202%2Fs00010%2F578a4921e61d4ac8a58c4e0986b27acc.jpg&h=eb684c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頻傳出現償債資金缺口的海航集團，彭博引述消息人士表示，旗下的香港國際建投（0687）正在與銀行商討再次延後其首筆的香港地產過橋貸款還款期。該筆貸款的現存餘額為28億元，整筆貸款原定需於去年11月償還，不過公司償還7億元後，獲延期一次至2月23日。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，香港國際建設尚未向銀行提交正式的延期計劃書，不過已經雙方已開始商討。如果海航不能再延期，貸款人有權取得土地控制權。海航拒絕置評。<br />\n<br />\n海航集團於啟德以272億元取得4幅土地，公司早前指第二筆過貸款已獲延期至7月15日，消息人士指第三和第四筆貸款將於2月和6月到期。早前市傳海航罕有地將2幅土地的發展注入基金，尋求外部投資者參與，每名投資最少100萬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1517558823519&amp;issue=20180202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1517558823519%26issue%3D20180202&d=Uy%2BW7RV8F6sDBdbTeXJrKxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2fbcd3fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1517558823519%26issue%3D20180202&h=a3f8e968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1517558823519&amp;issue=20180202</a>"},{"pid":"0319877a195a273fda906f08ae83e0460a63606a","tid":548163,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連黨報都開始吹海航唔掂"},{"pid":"1a67443a9edca38205e719f4c8e82ca9436b2b7f","tid":548163,"uid":5172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:04:15.000Z","msg":"貪撚左咁多，比人食曬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7066efb968e58ab0f4383c84eae250fc42f7972","tid":548163,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"爆啦屌你老母,我等緊機會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6d557aa3ffc14293560430964df5a58fdb55d2","tid":548163,"uid":111909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"乞兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01d26192bec37a68e8aa34cd9d62eef7857fb6f","tid":548163,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c6f807788b7490282ba40f4760f5f26190081a","tid":548163,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"新地食緊花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n攞多d野黎同我換錢，你急我唔急<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0011b6e4036e8022c7013f3134b08c3a019aa009","tid":548163,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}